text:
Since a lot of the "founding fathers" are maybe lingering here today, I need to express a sincere thank you to all of you for your work. My python work has been putting bread on the table to provide for my family for 10 years now. I am so grateful towards all of you brilliant people that helped transform the world, but also the lives of ordinary folk like me.

From the bottom of my heart, thank you! üôè
